Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.06,0:24:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.15,0:24:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.82,0:24:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熟悉的制服 熟悉的太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.24,0:24:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那张面容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.66,0:24:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方干什么呢 土方君
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
